Subscribe to Get Report Notifications in Salesforce Classic

You can subscribe to a report instead of manually running it, and set conditions for notifications. You can also attach files to subscriptions.
Subscribe to Reports in Lightning Experience
Instead of manually running and emailing a report to your team, you can subscribe to a report.

Get Notified When Report Conditions Are Met
Set report conditions so that recipients are notified when a total in your Salesforce report reaches a meaningful threshold.

Schedule Reports in Salesforce Classic
You can set up a report to run itself daily, weekly, or monthly and send the results automatically to the people who need them.
